title: It’s Annoying I Want To Eat People - Novel Updates
tags: Female Protagonist   Misunderstandings   Non-humanoid Protagonist   Post-apocalyptic   Zombies
author: 甲川乙川
description:
Ordinary zombies roam the streets.

Foodie zombies worry about dwindling rations all day long.

Grumpy zombies think about how to occupy new territories.

As a unique zombie, Yan Han sleeps, dreams, watches the sunset and falls in love with humans.>
